Description copied from interface: ComputerInterface
reads the data out of the divecomputer.

Specified by:
transfer in interface ComputerInterface
Parameters:
status - The interface to show progress information to the user.
logbook - The actual opened logbook
Throws:
TransferException - if an error occured during transfer of the data from the dive computer.
NotInitializedException - if initialized has not been called before.
InvalidConfigurationException - if the configuration has an error, e.g. the specified interface doesn't exist, or the wrong computer is attached.
